{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act37side_level_act37side_05_end","storyGroup":"act37side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act37side_level_act37side_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GO-5","storyName":"废铁与铆钉","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"维娜为了解决城里各种矛盾而焦头烂额，好在格拉斯哥帮依旧陪在她的身边给予她力所能及的协助。希勒少尉因伤病而痛苦，戴菲恩及时出现，承诺带他回到丽茵卡登。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act37side/level_act37side_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act37side_05","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["夸夸其谈的男人","海蒂","埃利西奥","黛安","维娜","奥伦","戴菲恩","因陀罗","达格达","摩根","疗养院患者","希勒少尉","路人的声音","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_bg_34_g5_noblehall.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":9},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","duration":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"我还是很难想象，海蒂小姐。我们好不容易回到了这座伟大的城市，你却又要离开。","id":12,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"不过，也许你是该回到你父亲的身边了。","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"回到多伦郡吗？......嗯，说不定我会走得更远一些。毕竟，我生命中的领路人，可不止我父亲一位呀。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"当然，您的建议也总能启发我。例如您讲述的，与那位马奇伯爵的使者共进晚宴的经历，就让我学到不少知识。","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","focus":"m","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"哈哈，您这样一位远离政治的小说家想要写一些历史情节，我当然愿意提供一手资料。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"又例如您刚才说的，将我最熟悉的故乡多伦郡，与伦蒂尼姆这骇人听闻的战争一并写进故事里。","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","focus":"m","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"没错。要坦诚地回忆那段不甚体面的时光当然不容易，但我们为这座城市所做的英雄之举总该被人记住。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"英雄......您说得对，或许我们都算是英雄。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"对了，这样的爱情故事一定很迷人。远在维多利亚边境的少女与来此度假的青年一见钟情，但青年死在了伦蒂尼姆的战场上。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"当然，少女最终发现自己听到的消息是假的，爱人成为了英雄，回到了她的身边。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","focus":"m","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"这想法很好，海蒂小姐，失而复得的爱人，正如这座被外人践踏又被我们拯救的城市。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"......他们开始奏乐了。听啊，虽然宴会上没有红酒与甜点，灯火也不如过去那么明亮，但铜管中流淌出的音乐不会变得沙哑。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"请您移步舞池吧，将您提供的灵感和我都留在这窗台边就好。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","focus":"m","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"那请问您的这两位朋友——","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":36},{"type":"charslot","id":37},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":39},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","duration":"1.5","id":40},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":41},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"呃......","id":43},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"charslot","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"这位来自异国他乡的使者恐怕还不熟悉维多利亚的礼仪，您就放过他吧？","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_176","focus":"m","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夸夸其谈的男人","text":"哈哈，当然。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_176.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":51},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1.5","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":53},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"......","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":56},{"type":"charslot","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":58},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......海蒂小姐。这是您的名字，是吗？","id":60},{"type":"dialog","id":61},{"type":"charslot","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"——啊。我可以带你们四处走走。","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"charslot","id":66},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"不，不用再麻烦您了，刚才多谢您替我们解围。","id":69},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"charslot","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"事实上，这里从不拒绝任何客人，如果两位有兴趣，下次可以从客厅的大门走进来，而不是窗台。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":74},{"type":"charslot","id":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":76},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"谢谢您的好意。但......其实我对贵族们的宴会没有那么大的兴趣。","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"维多利亚的贵族政治是我最先调查的内容，我很清楚你们的礼仪、对感染者的态度，甚至那种舞步我都学过......","id":79},{"type":"dialog","id":80},{"type":"charslot","id":81},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"唔，先不说我这样一个三流小说家是否敢自诩贵族......您问过身边这位士兵，她为什么把您带到这里来吗？","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"charslot","id":85},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":86},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"——不，不是她带我来的，是我自作主张！","id":88},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黛安","text":"唉。海蒂小姐，对不起。他说想留在伦蒂尼姆，更深入地了解我们的感染者问题，所以我想带他到处看看......偶尔用些不太正当的办法。","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黛安","text":"您想笑话他的话可以直接笑，他就是这样不会说谎也藏不住心事的人。","id":91},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"charslot","id":93},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"呵呵，很像他的身份......“赤心”。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"埃利西奥先生，您是赤心医疗的代表，对吗？","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":97},{"type":"charslot","id":98},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":99},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"我不记得我们机构有这么大的名气......","id":101},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"charslot","id":103},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"对感染者问题有兴趣的人，总是很好认的。","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1c/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"不过，辨认贵族们默契的谎言，恐怕就没那么容易了。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"——比如说，正挽着手进入舞池的人，大半都是感染者。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":109},{"type":"charslot","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":111},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"这从理论上是可预期的，萨卡兹散布的源石粉尘伤害了所有伦蒂尼姆市民，不论身份高低。可是......","id":115},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"charslot","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"没有人会说破的。没有人会去探究站在自己身边的人是不是感染者，这是他们为自己保留的体面，也是......一种梦想。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":120},{"type":"charslot","id":121},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......","id":124},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"charslot","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"埃利西奥望向大厅。墙柱上残留着金饰被剥去后留下的坑洼，证明战争的暴徒曾踏足此地，但乐手们倾情的演奏几乎掩盖了眼前的萧条。","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"自称小说家的女士旋开钢笔的笔帽，在笔记本上潦草地写下了什么。","id":128},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"当然，您可以认为在温饱都成问题的时候，这些只是毫无意义的自我安慰。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":131},{"type":"charslot","id":132},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......不，当然不会。","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"只是一种生活与另一种生活。","id":136},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"charslot","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":139},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":141},{"type":"charslot","id":142},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":143},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"——这是？","id":145},{"type":"dialog","id":146},{"type":"charslot","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"刚刚随手记下的，一个不值一读的故事梗概......和一点额外的信息，请您收下。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6f/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"我有一种预感，埃利西奥先生，我们会再见面的。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":152},{"type":"charslot","id":153},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1519_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":154},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"......谢谢。","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_487_bobb_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃利西奥","text":"不过，请容许我额外过问一句——您似乎有什么痛苦，并不能被眼前的幻想安慰。","id":158},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"charslot","id":160},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":161},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":162},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":163},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"......我只是时不时想念我的一位朋友。","id":165,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/72/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_400_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海蒂","text":"她不在之后，能与我说真话的人又少了一位。","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_400_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":168},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"charslot","id":171},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"showall","id":172},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":173},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_darkness_03_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":174,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":176},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":177},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"“万国峰会”......？","id":179},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"拉特兰方面非常关注维多利亚发生的事情，毕竟这是一场萨卡兹造成的灾难。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"但您和议会当下在处理流窜萨卡兹问题上的果断，的确让我看到了这座城市复苏的希望。","id":182,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"当然，教宗阁下也衷心希望为泰拉诸国搭建和平议事的桥梁，以避免生灵涂炭的惨象再度出现。","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"......不过，你也不只是代表拉特兰教宗阁下来征求我的答复吧。","id":185},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我只是一个信使，只负责把消息原封不动地递交到您和议会的手上。","id":187,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"好，那麻烦替我向教宗阁下表达歉意。我明白拉特兰的善意，但现在议会顾不上伦蒂尼姆之外的事情。","id":189},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"以及，把我的话传给招待你的那位大公爵——我不会以任何身份前往拉特兰。至于他自己的打算，又什么时候轮到议会或者我过问了？","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_355_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"当然，这本就是信使的工作。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/00/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":195},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"2","id":196},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":197},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":198},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":199},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":200},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":201},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"2","id":202},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":203},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":204},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"奥伦·亚吉奥拉斯。根据情报，战争期间他曾身处高多汀公爵的高速军舰，但并未直接代表拉特兰参战。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"和我想的差不多。高多汀本人是不是也喜欢吃甜的？","id":208},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#7$1","focus":"l","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"如果真是那样，现在的伦蒂尼姆可拿不出多少东西招待他。","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"唉......难得今天是议会的休息日。","id":212},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"......比较有趣的边角消息是，那位拉特兰信使当时领了一队难民和他一起登舰，为了说服公爵接收难民，他将手搭在铳械上发誓。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"然后呢？","id":216},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"然后他的手被过热的铳管烫了个泡。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"哈。怎么突然说这个，很重要吗？","id":220},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"休息日。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_4110_delphn_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"好吧，那么这就算我休息过了。接下来我该先看哪边的消息？对法阵残迹的调查？","id":224},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_paper2","volume":"1","id":226},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":227},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"嗯？","id":229},{"type":"dialog","id":230},{"type":"charslot","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"维娜看到了希勒少尉的名字。又一封信。","id":232},{"type":"text","text":"她叹了口气，将信件放进了待办事项的筐里。","id":233},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":234},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4110_delphn_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"戴菲恩，这有——","id":236},{"type":"dialog","id":237},{"type":"charslot","id":238},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":239},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":240},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_155_tiger_1#1$1","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"-100,0","duration":"1.5","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":242},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_405_1#3$1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,0","duration":"1.5","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":244},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_comedy_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":245,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_155_tiger_1#1$1","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"-100,0","focus":"l","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"喂，维娜！你说的那帮抢东西的混蛋，我们抓出来好好教训过了！","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_155_tiger_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"专门打劫体弱的矿石病中晚期患者，实在让人不齿。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_avg_npc_396_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_405_1#3$1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,0","focus":"r","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"更叫人恶心的是，还有不少欺软怕硬的家伙被他们的名号吸引，想要加入。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_405_1#12$1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,0","focus":"r","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"幸好你这里消息灵通，没给他们发展起来的机会。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_405_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"charslot","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"唉，我真想自己也能出去活动一下。","id":257},{"type":"dialog","id":258},{"type":"charslot","id":259},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_155_tiger_1#1$1","posfrom":"-100,0","posto":"-100,0","focus":"l","id":260},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_396_1#13$1","focus":"l","id":261},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_405_1#12$1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"100,0","focus":"l","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"放心，连着你的份一起揍了。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_155_tiger_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"还有，收上来的谢礼，也留了你的一份。","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_avg_155_tiger_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"charslot","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1019_siege2_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"等等，这可不是去收保护费的活儿——","id":268},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"charslot","id":272},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":273},{"type":"image","image":"55_i06_2","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":274},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"85","block":"false","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"从回到维多利亚开始，你有多久没吃糖了？","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"因陀罗......","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"那个被打劫的小子说是他自己做的，每根都是不一样的怪味，正好你也不喜欢普通的甜味棒棒糖，对吧。","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"可他说为了代替自己搞不到的标准糖精，尝试了土豆、胡萝卜、地下通道源石虫体液......","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"我都试过，没问题的！","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"听上去可以提神。能不能给我也尝尝？","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"管够！","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"......你感觉还好吗，维娜？","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"没事，现在吃到什么都习惯了。","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"那......议长的事务呢？","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"对啊，你在操心什么呢，法令草案？公文？报告信？","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"还有没有什么活儿要我们帮忙干的？尤其是你自己不方便出手揍一顿的那种！","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"这次我还收了个跟班呢！那家伙虽然瘦得像草秆一样，但我也不是不能教他自保的拳术。","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"因陀罗","text":"格拉斯哥帮也该重新发展壮大了，维娜，我们什么时候能回——","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"达格达","text":"......","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"......","id":294},{"type":"text","text":"因陀罗挠了挠头。就算同伴不用埋怨的眼神看着她，她自己也反应过来了。她不该问的。","id":295},{"type":"text","text":"维娜的目光扫过桌面堆积如山的文件。","id":296},{"type":"text","text":"戴菲恩走到她身边，不动声色地从她手里抽出那几页信纸。","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"我想，也许是时候公开答复许多市民关心的问题了。绝大多数人不可能来旁听议会的讨论，但总会在一天的辛劳结束后听听收音机。","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"城内的状况已经逐渐稳定，我已经向议会申请派遣第三批工程队进入诺伯特区。很快，我们的家就会恢复到过去的样子了。","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"摩根","text":"是比过去更好！","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"维娜","text":"等剩下的这些事处理完，很快你也可以回丽茵卡登了，戴菲恩。","id":301},{"type":"dialog","id":302},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":303},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":305},{"type":"charslot","id":306},{"type":"image","id":307},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_bg_43_g7_towngreenhouse.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":308},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":309},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_saferoom_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":310,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":312},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":313},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":314},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":315},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"2","id":316},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":318},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":319},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"欸？黛安——","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"......长官？！","id":322},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"2","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","posfrom":"200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"2","id":325},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":327},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"我已经退役了......莎拉女士。","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"哈，好吧，长官。","id":331,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"我记得您之前拒绝了疗养院的邀请，这次您是......","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......不，只是来探望你们，也再次向你道谢......请不要介意。","id":337},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"其实我已经记不得了。您知道的，医生说那些石头已经到了我的头里了——您的手在抖。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"不必在我面前隐藏，长官，您教过我很多知识。幸好这些我都还记得。","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"看上去像是某种药物成瘾的症状。也是战时落下的毛病？","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......止痛剂过量。就城墙下那次落下的小毛病。","id":343},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"——！","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"您必须得留下。我去找疗养院的医生，他们说不定有办法......","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"或者至少，至少能尽可能帮您找到点——","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"更多的止痛剂？呵，的确能缓解些痛苦。","id":349},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"您就是为了这个才来的对吧？虽然城里物资的确都很紧缺，但说不定院长会愿意为您尽可能拨出来一些。","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"毕竟戴菲恩阁下一直很关照疗养院，也很照顾我们。","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":354},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"请稍等我一下，我马上回来。","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_avg_npc_418_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":357},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":358},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"2","id":359},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":360},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":361},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":363},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"text","text":"他想要留下，这样他或许真的能够拿到些已经不够再配发给他的止痛剂。","id":365},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1520_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"呼——","id":367},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":369},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"2.5","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"1.5","id":371},{"type":"delay","time":"4.5","id":372},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":373},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_418_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","duration":"2","id":374},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","afrom":"0","ato":"1","duration":"1.5","id":375},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疗养院患者","text":"欸......人呢？","id":377},{"type":"dialog","id":378},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":379},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":380},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":381},{"type":"charslot","id":382},{"type":"image","id":383},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"showall","id":384},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":385},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":386,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":387},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":388},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":389},{"type":"bg","duration":"3.5","from":"0","to":"1","block":"true","id":390},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","text":"","id":391},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":392},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":393},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":394},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"路人的声音","text":"喂，走路不看路吗！","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"路人的声音","text":"你离他远点，没看见他不对劲吗？","id":398},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"议长办公室，应该在......这边......嘶......","id":399},{"type":"dialog","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"1","id":402},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":403},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":404},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"路人的声音","text":"他倒了！又是个矿石病末期的倒霉蛋？","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"路人的声音","text":"别靠近了！要是他崩解了，我们都完蛋......","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......我......不是......啧，快控制不了身体了。","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"路人的声音","text":"我去叫人来！都散开，散开！","id":409},{"type":"dialog","id":410},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":411},{"type":"delay","time":"3.5","text":"","id":412},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":413},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":414},{"type":"charslot","id":415},{"type":"image","id":416},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_bg_47_g15_eveningglow_L1.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":417},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":418},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":420},{"type":"text","text":"希勒少尉躺倒在街道上，落日的光线并不刺眼，却依旧照得他眼睛发涩......","id":421},{"type":"text","text":"或者说，他的身体又在提醒他了——痛苦需要靠另一种生理性的渴望填补。","id":422},{"type":"text","text":"他试着调整呼吸，就像他过去手把手辅导那些在战争中被痛苦击败的士兵一样......","id":423},{"type":"text","text":"但他失败了，他早已被痛苦击倒。","id":424},{"type":"text","text":"希勒看到了火，炽热得让他难以继续睁开双眼。天边的火，城墙上的火，在他的躯体上燃烧的火——","id":425},{"type":"dialog","id":426},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":427},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":428},{"type":"bg","duration":"1","from":"1","to":"0","block":"true","id":429},{"type":"image","image":"55_i07_2","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":430},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":431},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":432},{"type":"text","text":"他好像看到了自己倒在城墙之下的那一天。","id":433},{"type":"text","text":"伦蒂尼姆的雄伟城墙在德拉克的火焰之中熊熊燃烧，那火焰越来越旺，越来越刺眼，直到吞噬了天空。","id":434},{"type":"text","text":"他害怕地嘶吼，他试图遮挡自己的双眼——","id":435},{"type":"dialog","id":436},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":437,"musicid":5},{"type":"cg","duration":"1","id":438,"from":"0","to":"1","block":"true"},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":439},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":440},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......少尉......","id":441},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"希勒......少尉......快......起......","id":442},{"type":"dialog","id":443},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"——？","id":444},{"type":"dialog","id":445},{"type":"cg","duration":"3.5","id":446,"from":"1","to":"0","block":"true"},{"type":"text","text":"他看到了一只手伸向了自己。","id":447},{"type":"dialog","id":448},{"type":"image","image":"55_i07_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2.5","id":449},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":450},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"戴......戴菲恩小姐？","id":451},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我一直在等你找我，少尉。","id":452},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我看到了你寄给维娜的信......但你故意避开了我，就像你拒绝了我为你提供治疗的帮助。","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......她最后也没看我的信......对吧，戴菲恩小姐？","id":454},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我能猜到你在信里写了什么。","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":456},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"抱歉，但在这，我的确帮不上你。伦蒂尼姆的药物供应情况我们都很清楚，所以你不能留在这。","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......我，还能去哪？","id":458},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"丽茵卡登。","id":459},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"——不！我......","id":460},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"这不是请求，是命令，少尉。也不必用你已经退役的那套说辞来搪塞我。","id":461},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我知道你在犹豫什么，在害怕什么。","id":462},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"你害怕面对“加拉瓦铁盾”那些背叛和抛弃了你的长官们......","id":463},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"害怕没能履行对我，还有对我妈妈的忠诚，更害怕以如今这副样子回到家乡，不是吗？","id":464},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"我......不知道......","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"少尉，你没有自己想的那么强大和坚强，我也没有你认为的那么脆弱和高贵。","id":466},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我们都是丽茵卡登人......这里本就不是我们的家。","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"战争已经结束了，少尉。士兵都应归乡。","id":468},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"不用怕，少尉，我会陪你一起回家。","id":470},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"走吧。","id":471},{"type":"dialog","id":472},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":473},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":474},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"charslot","id":476},{"type":"image","id":477},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/be/Avg_bg_47_g15_eveningglow_L2.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":478},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":479},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":480},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":481},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"（呜咽）可我这副样子......还怎么能坚持到回家呀......","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我会安排的。再说，你不会以为你不找我，我真就会完全放任你不管吧？","id":483},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......谢谢您，戴菲恩小姐......","id":484},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"那您，还会回伦蒂尼姆吗？","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"会，这也是我对维娜的承诺。不过，恐怕得辛苦她等上一段时间了。","id":486},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"我先安置你在城内疗养，等我处理完手里最后的事情，我们就出发吧。","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"希勒少尉","text":"......遵命，戴菲恩小姐。","id":488},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"丽茵卡登......我也要回家了，妈妈。","id":489},{"type":"dialog","id":490},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":491},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":493},{"type":"charslot","id":494},{"type":"image","id":495}],"characters":["夸夸其谈的男人","海蒂","埃利西奥","黛安","维娜","奥伦","戴菲恩","因陀罗","达格达","摩根","疗养院患者","希勒少尉","路人的声音","？？？"]}